  dialogue:
  - Heyyy! Up and at 'em hero~ you've got a gut to fill and a guild to shock today!
  - 'Hows the mood? You''ve been working for this moment for a long long time.

    Nerves
    have gotta be going crazy. What''s the feel? Hungry? Antsy? Need to fight? I''ve
    got this crazy robot training dummy I''ve been itching to test!'
  responses:
  - unPauser: 1
    responseText: Nerves? Pshh!
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4c232274ad09b9f419d3b433a0eee620, type: 2}
  - unPauser: 1
    responseText: Shaking a little!
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 47c1f0a0e6ff9f64a9d99c374cf8faae, type: 2}
  - unPauser: 1
    responseText: ROBOT TRAINING DUMMY?!
    dialogueObject: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8e7b6531f52f44541b86c5e2e6aae335, type: 2}
